  "body": "## Description\r\n\r\nThis issue serves to track the state of the validator client.\r\n\r\nIt is a `mega-issue`, therefore if you wish to work on some task here, leave a comment and it will be split into a new issue.\r\n\r\n## Known issues\r\n\r\n- `ChainSpec` is fixed to foundation; it should be loaded from disk or generated at first boot.\r\n- Validator public keys are randomly generated at boot; they should be loaded from file.\r\n- Persistence of signed message is not implemented, therefore slash-safety is not present.\r\n- `eth2/attester` crate needs to be implemented as a service.\r\n- `genesis_time` needs to be pulled from the Beacon Node.\r\n- Domains need to be accurately generated (#240)\r\n",
